						               													<description>Legacy of Atmos is a game of epic tactical skirmish-based warfare for 2-4 players with deck-building elements and a character fate and alignment system!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will command a small force of legendary Characters and models that are fighting a battle which forms part of the larger on-going conflict. &amp;#10;This box set&amp;rsquo;s release follows the events of Highlord Godrey Ronin and his crusade against the mysterious Tellus Commune.&amp;#10;Will you choose to defend the mystical Tellus Forest, with their strange creatures and savage Karath Tribes, or pursue Godrey&amp;rsquo;s quest for his House's vengeance?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played by first selecting your Legendary Character and building your army and deck list. Players will fight over zones of control that increase their Supremacy Points at the end of each round. Each player will also bring with them 3 secret &amp;quot;Gambits&amp;quot; with them into a game.  These Gambits support an intense variety of playstyles and gives the player Supremacy Points when completed. The player with the most Supremacy Points at the end of 5 battle rounds wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
